## Elay Backend ‚Äî .NET Commands

This is a **C# / .NET** solution (`Elay.sln`). Prefer these RTK-wrapped commands:

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Build (compact) | `rtk dotnet build Elay.sln` |
| Build single project | `rtk dotnet build Customer/Api/Api.csproj` |
| Test (compact) | `rtk dotnet test` |
| Restore | `rtk dotnet restore Elay.sln` |
| Format | `rtk dotnet format` |
| EF migrations list | `rtk err dotnet ef migrations list --project Customer/Infrastructure` |

RTK has native `dotnet` subcommands: `build`, `test`, `restore`, `format`.
For other `dotnet` commands (e.g. `ef`), use `rtk err dotnet <cmd>`.

